Correlations between All-Block All-Target Outcome Measures vs NARA

corr_ct <- cor.test(all_blocks$Total_Time, all_blocks$NARA)
corr_ct
## 
##  Pearson's product-moment correlation
## 
## data:  all_blocks$Total_Time and all_blocks$NARA

##  -0.68641361 -0.02377631
